title: Sibling Watchery: Drag Race Season 8 Episode 4
description:
Monét and Bob review Season 8 Episode 4 of Drag Race as the queens took to the stage to sing live in a 1980s-style salute to New Wave girl bands.
See Monét and Bob on tour this summer by going to bobandmonet.com !!
